id: jf-w5ow
title: Align Toon documentation with the emitted type and data envelope
description: "The Toon guide promises a meta object containing timestamp, format, and version, and repeats it in 31 examples. The actual formatter emits only the stable type and compact data envelope. This false contract can break consumers that require nonexistent fields."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: agents,documentation,output-contract,toon
created_at: "2026-07-16T16:57:06.816Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-16T17:00:22.194Z"
