author: codex
acceptance_criteria: Overview and structure sections describe only type and data.; No example includes the nonexistent meta envelope.
goal: jf-mqpo
parent: jf-fdh1
severity: high
environment: docs/toon-format.md versus src/formatters/base.ts
resolution: "Removed all 31 nonexistent meta examples, corrected the overview and TypeScript interface, and retained the canonical type/data contract."
expected_result: Documentation demonstrates only fields emitted by formatToon.
actual_result: Guide and formatter are aligned; repository search finds no stale meta envelope claims.
customer_impact: Automation may reject valid CLI output or rely on timestamp/version fields that are always absent.
